00:11:52.78 --> 00:11:57.06
CBS's Ian Lee is in London with more.

00:11:57.06 --> 00:11:59.85
Prince Andrew's legal battle with Virginia Giuffre

00:11:59.85 --> 00:12:02.88
ended today when the two reached a financial settlement

00:12:02.88 --> 00:12:04.92
