00:19:48.33 --> 00:19:51.40
of why claims from sick veterans exposed to contaminated

00:19:51.40 --> 00:19:53.74
drinking water at a North Carolina military base

00:19:53.74 --> 00:19:55.15
are being denied.

00:19:55.15 --> 00:19:57.19
Well, that's tonight's CBS Evening News.

00:19:57.19 --> 00:19:58.92
Good night.

